Qt Hldplugin version 3.3.2 contains bug fixes.

The most important changes are listed in this document. For a complete
list of changes, see the Git log for the Qt Hldplugin sources that
you can check out from the public Git repository. For example:

git clone git://gitorious.org/qt-hldplugin/qt-hldplugin.git
git log --cherry-pick --pretty=oneline v3.3.1..v3.3.2

C++ Support
   * Fixed deployment of Clang code model plugin (QTHLDPLUGINBUG-14038)

Qt Quick Designer
   * Fixed crash of Qt Quick emulation layer when using fallback emulation
     (QTHLDPLUGINBUG-14031)
